[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "结束测试和芙提雅一起回到世界树，已经是晚上了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "内部开发委员会此时刚结束评审讨论，正等待着我们过去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然他们前期没有批准项目开发，但芙提雅自行造出原型还提交了完整的书面报告与视频资料，按规章制度也是必须给予回复的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "据我得到的消息，芙提雅那门违规的射线炮惊艳到了所有的见证者。委员会这些顽固的家伙也不例外。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看来，我们现在过去，一定能得到好消息吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "感谢你陪我这么久呀，分析员。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但等会儿，你就能看到委员会那些家伙不情愿地承认我的发明的样子了，哼哼，肯定很有意思。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们走吧~！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "委员会的三名评审，早已在里面坐定。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而他们的表情，一个比一个凝重。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我心中泛起了一阵不好的预感……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "评审1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这件外骨骼，还没有名字是吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "评审1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "单兵武器能发挥这么大的威力，实在出人意料，我们对此都很肯定。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "评审2",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "评审2",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "巨大的威力意味着巨大的功耗，它在不充能的前提下，能开几发？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "评审3",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而且这个重量，让它显得有些拙劣了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "评审1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "最重要的是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "评审1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芙提雅·伊格妮丝，你作为天启者中的精英，我们认为你应该将重点放在研究如何利用泰坦力量上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "评审3",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没错，请问你能给出非得坚持研发这部外骨骼的理由吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我本以为芙提雅马上会开始长篇大论的反驳，但我错了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的脸上写满了倔强和不甘，却并无言语。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我马上想起了之前在车间的时候，芙提雅给我讲述的事……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "要说一定要坚持的原因……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员你肯定不知道我为什么加入前线部门吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "原先的我啊，成天泡在实验室里，对亲自上阵其实没什么兴趣……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但有一次，我在实验室里，无意看到了逐光者的深夜“狩猎”直播。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那是一场……每次想到就会心痛的惨剧……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "他们的无人机装上了不知哪里得来的新型机枪，并使用它在与郊狼的交战中大获全胜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "到这里，还算正常……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "直播末尾，一名幸存郊狼女性成员扔下武器逃跑，逐光者的无人机紧随其后，用子弹惊吓她、调戏她，但……偏偏不杀死她……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "摄像机频繁抓拍逃跑者恐慌的脸，那些直播的逐光者们，笑得如同恶魔……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "最终，逃跑者体力耗尽，跪在地上苦苦求饶，并拿出一张照片，以证明自己是一名孩子的母亲。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然而，他们发射的子弹穿过照片……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "即使只是在回忆，我也能清楚感受到芙提雅哽咽中的愤怒。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而她的眼神中，更是写满了坚定。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我应该为此负起责任……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不……",
        "disable": 0
