        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "b-2-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这不是你应该背负的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好了啦，分析员你这个老好人，就别安慰我了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这就是我的责任。百分之百。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为逐光者无人机上使用的AI操控引擎，就是我研发的“火种引擎”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说到这，她深深叹了口气。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "之后我展开过调查，利用无人机作恶其实并不是个例。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以，我应该为更多人开发足以自保和对抗恶势力的武器，让他们……不需要海姆达尔或者其他人介入，也能阻止那一小部分人的暴行！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "更何况，在神格天启之前，我也不过是个普通人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我很明白，力量不应该是极少数人的专利。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "委员会更重视已经应用的泰坦技术，我能理解，这是他们的职责。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但我依然认为，普通人也能使用的力量，一定是胜过极少数人才能使用的特权。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你说对吗，分析员！？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那时，我给予了芙提雅肯定的回答。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的意志十分了不起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如同神话中的普罗米修斯，“火种”为世人带来的一切，最终都成为了她的枷锁。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她没有屈服于此，而是不断地去努力着、抗争着……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但此情此景，或许她终于意识到了真正的桎梏何在。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "再绚烂而强大的炮火也只是一瞬间的光芒，打不破重重成见。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "再怎么美好的科技愿景，也难免被恶意之人歪曲与利用。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她身旁，不是还有我在吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
